\u8221\'1d . This information sheet has been prepared to explain why the research is being done and what it will involve. You can decide whether or not to take part. If you do decide to participate, you can change your mind at any time and are free to withdraw at any time, without giving a reason.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl560\slmult0\sb0\sa254{\cf1\b\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
What is the purpose of this study?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl480\slmult0\sb0\sa382{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
Ordinary everyday life is sometimes seen as too mundane or obvious to be documented, but in this way it is forgotten. Participating in this project will help me, and any future researchers who re-examine the recording, to understand some of the context and user experiences that are not recorded elsewhere. This will contribute to a richer history of domestic chemicals than can be }{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
researched}{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
 simply from industrial history or promotional materials and objects, so in this way collecting oral histories will further the development of this field of research in social history.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl560\slmult0\sb0\sa254{\cf1\b\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
Why have I been invited to participate?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl480\slmult0\sb0\sa382{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
This is a study of everyday life, so your memories and experiences of shopping for and using chemicals or chemical products in your home or garden are of interest. Your participation will provide an aspect which is often missing from histories of technology: the perspective of the }{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
ordinary }{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
user.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl560\slmult0\sb0\sa254{\cf1\b\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
What will happen if I take part?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl480\slmult0\sb0\sa382{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
Sharing memories and thoughts about household tasks and hobbies involving chemicals (or perhaps deciding against using certain chemicals), talking more generally about the time period in question, of the personal experiences of using products could be quite a pleasant way to spend an hou}{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
r or two}{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl480\slmult0\sb0\sa382{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
