ou }{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
may}{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
 have questions about the safety of products that you have used in the past. The aim of this historical study is to find out how you dealt with these questions as they came about and how they shaped your subsequent actions, rather than to provide information about the scientific effects of a diverse set of chemicals.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af7\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\sl560\slmult0\sb0\sa254{\cf1\b\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
