future }{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
researchers. The social history resource that you have helped to create will be valuable to academic researchers and for exhibition curators. }{\cf1\b0\afs24\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f5
